acknowledgements.message: A current Virtual Connect Manager configuration backup must be created. Virtual Connect Manager will not be available after the migration.
Any OneView resources created by or used during this migration must not be modified until the migration has completed.

issues.description: One or more connections for profile "Profile1" are configured with Use-BIOS boot settings. OneView does not support profile connections configured with a mixture of Use-BIOS and other boot settings.
issues.recommendation: The Virtual Connect Use-BIOS boot setting will be automatically changed to "not bootable" when the profile is migrated to OneView. If this change is acceptable, proceed with the migration.

issues.description: Ethernet connection 11 does not have an assigned network. This connection will not be migrated because OneView does not allow server profile connections without an assigned network.
issues.recommendation: If it is acceptable for this connection to not be migrated to the OneView server profile, proceed with the migration. {"name":"Learn more","uri":"/doc#/cic/enclosure/migrate/unassigned/connect/learn"}

issues.description: The network "1Network" is disabled and will be enabled in the OneView configuration.
issues.recommendation: If migrating the network as enabled is acceptable, continue with the migration. Alternatively, remove the network from the configuration before proceeding.
